OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FDavid Sullivan has stepped down as
OL,7,Fchairman of West Ham with immediate
OL,8,Feffect.
OL,10,FThe 77-year-old is leaving his role of
OL,11,F16 years to fight "false allegations"
OL,12,Fabout his private life.
OL,14,FHe said: "After very careful
OL,15,Fconsideration and with a heavy heart,
OL,16,FI have decided to resign as joint-
OL,17,Fchair and director of West Ham United
OL,18,FFC with immediate effect.
OL,26,@sD@SOUsD@eO]vD@JOU
