OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780916574
OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,F"This has been an incredibly painful
OL,7,Fdecision to make, but it is one made
OL,8,Fout of love, respect, and
OL,9,Fresponsibility toward a football club
OL,10,Fand a fan base that deserve absolute
OL,11,Funity and focus moving forward."
OL,13,FWest Ham announced that interim chief
OL,14,Fexecutive officer Karim Virani,
OL,15,Freporting into the current board of
OL,16,Fdirectors, will continue to be
OL,17,Fresponsible for leading the club's day-
OL,18,Fto-day operations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]
