OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FA club statement said: "West Ham
OL,7,FUnited can confirm that Joint-Chair
OL,8,FDavid Sullivan has stepped down from
OL,9,Fhis position with immediate effect.
OL,11,F"Mr Sullivan has also resigned as a
OL,12,Fdirector of both WH Holding Limited
OL,13,Fand West Ham United Football Club,
OL,14,Fhaving been made aware of the
OL,15,Fimpending publication of serious
OL,16,Fhistoric allegations.
OL,18,F"It is understood none of the
OL,19,Fallegations relate to West Ham United
OL,20,For any of its operations."
OL,26,@nD@XOUsD@AOUzD@AOU|D@ZO]
