OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780916574
OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FSullivan and business partner David
OL,7,FGold completed their takeover of West
OL,8,FHam after selling Birmingham, and
OL,9,Fbrought Karren Brady with them as vice-
OL,10,Fchairman.
OL,12,FTheir tenure oversaw the unpopular
OL,13,Fmove from Upton Park to the former
OL,14,FOlympic Stadium in 2016, making the
OL,15,Fthree of them the focus of numerous
OL,16,Fanti-board protests among club's
OL,17,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
