PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780916574
OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FGold died in 2023 aged 86, while
OL,7,FBaroness Brady left her role before
OL,8,Fthe end of a challenging season which
OL,9,Fended in relegation from the Premier
OL,10,FLeague.
OL,12,F"None of these allegations relate to
OL,13,Fmy more than 30 years in football,"
OL,14,Fadded Sullivan.
OL,16,F"West Ham United has been one of the
OL,17,Fgreatest passions and privileges of my
OL,18,Flife. I care deeply about the club,
OL,19,Fits supporters, its players, its
OL,20,Fstaff, and its future.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@cO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
