OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780916574
OL,3,CWest Ham chairman resigns with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,F"At what is already a challenging and
OL,7,Fimportant time for the club, I refuse
OL,8,Fto allow personal matters concerning
OL,9,Fme to become an unnecessary
OL,10,Fdistraction or a source of
OL,11,Finstability."
OL,13,FWest Ham say they will give "an update
OL,14,Fon the future structure of the board
OL,15,Fof directors in due course, but will
OL,16,Fmake no further comment at this time".
OL,18,FCzech businessman Daniel Kretinsky
OL,19,Fbought a 27 per cent stake in the club
OL,20,Fin 2021 and is reportedly set to
OL,21,Fincrease his stake.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@MO]uD@]OUxD@eO]
